Guide.title: Secret Waterfall Cave
Guide.Content: 1. Go to the Wobbly Statue on Jungle Island  Find a big rock in the shape of wobbly  EXTRA. Present  There will be a present behind the statue  2. The drooling wobbly  It will look like the wobbly drooled so much it turned into a river  3. The waterfall  Behind the first waterfall will be a cave  EXTRA. Dino bottoms secret  Thanks to Tingle Man, we all know where the dino is!  If you need help, look below this text In front of the waterfall there is a little island surrounded by the river (the river splits in half then goes back in a whole again). Then, there will be weird noises coming from that island. Find the dino then interact with it.

Guide.title: Spider Outfit
Guide.Content: Mountain base  Go to mountain base and find the lab with shrink ray  Table  When shrinked, go to the chess table, there will be a spider sitting on pizza  Come and go stage  Take the spider and run to place with beakers (wardrobe)  Highest floor of planks  Go inside hole, go to place with computer then go up one more floor  Door  On that floor you will see a door, take spider into door and mama spider will give you costume  What I wanna tell you  This took a lot of effort but it was worth it

Guide.title: cross the Temple puzzle
Guide.Content: How to get across  This is how you get across the puzzle maze in the temple that falls into water if you do it wrong. You start by walking on to the square that is second from the right, walk forward 1 square, walk left 1 square, walk forward 1 square, walk left 1 square, walk forward 2 squares, walk right 3 squares, walk forward 2 squares, walk left 1 square, then go straight until you finish crossing.

Guide.title: ALL secret pets!
Guide.Content: To get the ghost pet you first need to go to the temple in the jungle and go through it until you get to the part with the teal ball, you are going to need to complete the puzzle and get the ball. After the ball has been acquired bring it out of the temple (go back from where you came) and bring it to the waterfall (which is also in the jungle). Go behind the waterfall into the cave and once again go through it until you come across the ball puzzle, get the ball by completing the puzzle and leave with it. Once you have gotten both balls bring them to the mining job and leave them outside. Accept the job and break ores and explore until you find an ore that has a tunnel behind it. Once you do that quit that shift and go get the balls. Accept the job once again and bring the balls to that same ore.

Guide.title: The Hidden Cars
Guide.Content: How to find the hidden cars:  Rocket car: The rocket car is hidden in the cargo bay in side a red open container on the left side of the bay.  Motorcycle: The motorcycle is hidden in a shed filled with hay on the side of the left cow field.  Hamster ball: To get the Hamster ball head ball to the lab and go to the shrinking mashing then after your shrunk you go and push the button behind the boxes then reset. After that go back to the fan and it'll be turned off go into the vents and the hamster balls will be there.

Guide.title: Fast Travel
Guide.Content: What you need  To fast travel you need:  Propeller hat Fire hydraged (or in my words a fire extinguisher)  What to do  Grab a fire hydraged and turn on ur propeller hat on then u will be on the other side of the map in no time
